                     <interp inst="t18260406-312-person1677" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            . Q. How did you know he lived over the water? A. I received information from a young lad in the market; he had before that lived a long while in Shoreditch, with his mother; I have known him fifteen years; I thought him an honest lad</p>
               <p>GUILTY. Aged 19.</p>
